      <title>泰国称投资计划飙升至十年来最高水平 330 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thailand-says-investment-plans-soar-to-a-decade-high-33-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国表示，随着这个东南亚国家成为数据中心、云服务和先进电子制造的热门目的地，国内外公司去年承诺投资 1.14 万亿泰铢（330 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thailand-says-investment-plans-soar-to-a-decade-high-33-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:28:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应链转移致中国对越南出口首次超过日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国关税迫使企业寻找新的供应商以避免征税，同时继续依赖中国制造商提供零部件，越南首次超过日本成为中国第三大出口目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国内阁批准赌场法案草案 推动旅游业发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thai-cabinet-gives-conditional-nod-for-bill-to-legalize-casinos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁原则上批准了一项旨在使赌场合法化的法案，政府称此举是促进旅游业和打击东南亚国家猖獗的非法赌博行为的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thai-cabinet-gives-conditional-nod-for-bill-to-legalize-casinos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾抗议中国船只和直升机的“非法”行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/philippines-protests-illegal-presence-of-china-ships-chopper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周一表示，已向北京方面提起外交抗议，以抗议其在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫前夕南海局势再度紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/philippines-protests-illegal-presence-of-china-ships-chopper</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:25:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和持续的英国脱欧问题共同阻碍英国贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-and-ongoing-brexit-troubles-combine-to-threaten-uk-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿咨询集团周一发布的一份报告显示，从 2023 年开始的十年内，英国商品贸易年均增长率预计仅为 0.7%，远低于全球平均水平的 2.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-and-ongoing-brexit-troubles-combine-to-threaten-uk-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教堂集会支持陷入困境的杜特尔特，吸引了超过一百万人参加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/church-rally-backing-embattled-duterte-draws-more-than-a-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特的 100 多万支持者周一在首都举行集会，这一力量展示可能会迫使立法者驳回针对她的弹劾投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/church-rally-backing-embattled-duterte-draws-more-than-a-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯液化天然气货物运抵西班牙附近，测试最新制裁的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russian-lng-cargo-near-spain-to-test-impact-of-latest-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，一艘装载着从美国制裁的俄罗斯工厂运出的货物的液化天然气油轮，将首次考验买家规避最新一轮惩罚措施的意愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russian-lng-cargo-near-spain-to-test-impact-of-latest-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯面临越来越多的呼声，要求制定计划平息英国市场的紧张情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/reeves-returns-from-china-amid-calls-to-confront-uk-s-gilt-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 周一从中国返回英国，工党希望摆脱财政困难引起的市场动荡，并强调政府的长期目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/reeves-returns-from-china-amid-calls-to-confront-uk-s-gilt-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大规模集会聚焦莫迪印度教议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/the-world-s-largest-human-gathering-is-about-to-begin-in-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度将于周一举办十年一度的宗教活动，该活动被誉为世界上最大的人类聚会，为总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党提供了一个在数亿朝圣者中宣传印度民族主义议程的新机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/the-world-s-largest-human-gathering-is-about-to-begin-in-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普助手敦促乌克兰降低征兵年龄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/trump-aide-floats-push-for-ukraine-to-lower-military-draft-age</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的新政府的一名高级助手表示，在与俄罗斯达成任何协议之前，将要求乌克兰降低征兵年龄，以加强其战场地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/trump-aide-floats-push-for-ukraine-to-lower-military-draft-age</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:18:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
